  "name": "Blistering Invective",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>A heap of insults and invectives spew from your mouth-words so devastating your foes burn from the intensity of your diatribe. Your words deal @Damage[2d6[persistent,fire]] damage, and the target must attempt a Will save. If the target doesn't understand the language or you're not speaking a language, it gains a +4 circumstance bonus to its save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half the persistent fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1} and takes the full persistent fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 2} and takes double the persistent fire damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> You can target two additional creatures, and the persistent damage increases by [[/r 2d6]].</p>"
    },
